column2: They say cheaters never prosper, right? Show them otherwise with these buildings.
You need to control Rome, Madrid, Westminster, St. Peters, or Paris.
The Sipsist populace believe in the Real Guy, Sips. They follow an archive of his best sayings and doings.
the Real Guy, the Best Guy

The Cheat Order is a polytheistic religion based on no central god. They believe that any man who is powerful enough to gain the Cheat Empire and proclaim himself the God-King is the one true god. They believe that once the God-King has united the world under His Holiest Empire, all men and women shall live in peace and prosperity.
In order to create His Holiest Empire, you must first have 1000 Piety and be God reborn.
